                                          <title>Caret Down Icon</title>
                                          <path d="M18.3536 9.70709L12 16.0606L5.64648 9.70708L6.70714 8.64642L12 13.9393L17.2929 8.64643L18.3536 9.70709Z" fill="currentColor"></path>
